data.description: Well Kept And Breathtaking Home Nestled In The Desirable Summit North Neighborhood Only Minutes Away From Canyon Lake. Walking Inside You Will Be Taking In All The Intricate Details That Come Together Making This Home Special. The Floors Are Ceramic Wood Style Tile Laid Throughout. Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Raised Ceilings In Primary And Living Room, Marble Finishing In Primary Shower And The Large Soaking Tub, Not To Mention The Huge Walk-In Closest. Stepping Outside You'll Find Large Covered Front And Rear Patios, Both With Wood Ceiling Finishings And Flush Lighting. Additional Rock Landscaping Has Been Done To Help You Fully Utilize The Outdoor Space, With The Property Being Just Over A Half Acre You'll Have Plenty Of Elbow Room. Come See How This House Can Become Your Home.
